title: Carly Rae Jepsen Teases Music Video for Next Single 'Your Type'
text:
Comments The singer shares a photo from the Gia Coppola-directed video for her third 'E.Mo.Tion' single. 
Carly Rae Jepsen is releasing "Your Type" as the next single off her latest album, " E.Mo.Tion ". The Canadian beauty is currently readying the song's music video and has let fans take a peek into it via a still she shared on Twitter and Instagram on Monday, October 12. The photo shows Jepsen in what looks like an eatery. She stands still and looks sad as she stares straight at the camera. "Something's coming... #YourType," the 29-year-old singer wrote in the excited-sounding caption. — Carly Rae Jepsen (@carlyraejepsen) October 12, 2015 Produced by Rami Yacoub and Carl Falk, "Your Type" is the third official single following "I Really Like You" and "Run Away With Me" from Jepsen's critically-acclaimed album which was released in the U.S. in August. There's still no word on when the song will start impacting radio. Its accompanying visuals is directed by Gia Coppola and Jepsen's boyfriend David Kalani Larkins. The full video has yet to have an official release date.
